data.description: Beautiful, updated condo featuring a bright open floor plan, two primary suites and a bonus room often used as an office, nursery or playroom. Recent updates include new kitchen appliances (2024), new water heater (2024), new carpet (2024), fresh paint throughout & new light fixtures. Condo fees cover water, trash, sewer, community pool, walking paths, beautiful ground maintenance, clubhouse and more! Listing agent related to seller.
